<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge"><div class="pulse"></div> LIVE CONFLICT TRACKER</div>
  <h1>Current <em>Global Conflicts</em> 2025<br>& Market Impact</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Every major active war and armed conflict tracked in real time — with risk levels, casualty data, and market intelligence for investors and analysts.</p>
  <div class="conflict-count-bar">
    <div class="count-item">
      <div class="count-num red">56</div>
      <div class="count-label">Active Conflicts</div>
    </div>
    <div class="count-item">
      <div class="count-num amber">7</div>
      <div class="count-label">Major Wars</div>
    </div>
    <div class="count-item">
      <div class="count-num gold">3</div>
      <div class="count-label">Critical Risk</div>
    </div>
    <div class="count-item">
      <div class="count-num" style="color:var(--blue)">89s</div>
      <div class="count-label">Doomsday Clock</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CONFLICT CARDS -->
<div class="container">
  <div class="section-title">Major Active Conflicts — 2025–2026</div>

  <!-- UKRAINE -->
  <div class="conflict-card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <div class="conflict-flag">🇺🇦🇷🇺</div>
      <div class="card-header-text">
        <div class="card-title">Ukraine — Russia War</div>
        <div class="card-subtitle">Eastern Europe · Started February 2022 · Year 4</div>
      </div>
      <div class="risk-badge risk-critical">● CRITICAL</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">Est. Casualties</div>
          <div class="stat-value red">1.2M+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">Displaced Persons</div>
          <div class="stat-value gold">14.6M</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">NATO Involvement</div>
          <div class="stat-value blue">Active</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">Conflict Score</div>
          <div class="stat-value red">94/100</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="risk-bar-row">
        <div class="risk-bar-label">Nuclear Risk</div>
        <div class="risk-bar-track"><div class="risk-bar-fill" style="width:72%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--amber),var(--red))"></div></div>
        <div class="risk-bar-pct">72%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="risk-bar-row">
        <div class="risk-bar-label">Escalation Risk</div>
        <div class="risk-bar-track"><div class="risk-bar-fill" style="width:85%;background:var(--red)"></div></div>
        <div class="risk-bar-pct">85%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="risk-bar-row">
        <div class="risk-bar-label">Market Impact</div>
        <div class="risk-bar-track"><div class="risk-bar-fill" style="width:91%;background:var(--red)"></div></div>
        <div class="risk-bar-pct">91%</div>
      </div>

      <p class="card-desc" style="margin-top:16px">Russia's full-scale invasion of Ukraine, now entering its fourth year, remains the most significant conventional land war in Europe since World War II. The front line has stabilized along a 1,000km front in eastern and southern Ukraine. Peace negotiations remain stalled, with both sides hardening positions in 2025. NATO has dramatically increased aid, with F-16 fighter jets now operational in Ukrainian service.</p>

      <div class="market-impact">
        <div class="market-impact-title">⚡ Market Impact — Ukraine War</div>
        <div class="impact-items">
          <div class="impact-item"><span class="impact-commodity">European Natural Gas (TTF)</span><span class="impact-effect up">+340% vs pre-war</span></div>
          <div class="impact-item"><span class="impact-commodity">Global Wheat Prices</span><span class="impact-effect up">+28% elevated</span></div>
          <div class="impact-item"><span class="impact-commodity">Fertilizer (Potash/Urea)</span><span class="impact-effect up">+65% vs 2021</span></div>
          <div class="impact-item"><span class="impact-commodity">Defense Stocks (LMT, RTX, BA)</span><span class="impact-effect up">+80-120% since 2022</span></div>
          <div class="impact-item"><span class="impact-commodity">EUR/USD Exchange Rate</span><span class="impact-effect down">Persistent weakness</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- GAZA / ISRAEL -->
  <div class="conflict-card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <div class="conflict-flag">🇮🇱🇵🇸</div>
      <div class="card-header-text">
        <div class="card-title">Israel — Gaza War</div>
        <div class="card-subtitle">Middle East · Started October 2023 · Year 2</div>
      </div>
      <div class="risk-badge risk-critical">● CRITICAL</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">Gaza Casualties</div>
          <div class="stat-value red">48,000+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">Displaced</div>
          <div class="stat-value gold">1.9M</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">Regional Spread</div>
          <div class="stat-value blue">Lebanon, Yemen</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-label">Conflict Score</div>
          <div class="stat-value red">88/100</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="risk-bar-row">
        <div class="risk-bar-label">Iran Escalation</div>
        <div class="risk-bar-track"><div class="risk-bar-fill" style="width:78%;background:var(--red)"></div></div>
        <div class="risk-bar-pct">78%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="risk-bar-row">
        <div class="risk-bar-label">Oil Supply Risk</div>
        <div class="risk-bar-track"><div class="risk-bar-fill" style="width:65%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),var(--amber))"></div></div>
        <div class="risk-bar-pct">65%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="risk-bar-row">
        <div class="risk-bar-label">Shipping Risk</div>
        <div class="risk-bar-track"><div class="risk-bar-fill" style="width:82%;background:var(--amber)"></div></div>
        <div class="risk-bar-pct">82%</div>
      </div>

      <p class="card-desc" style="margin-top:16px">The Israel-Hamas war that began with the October 7, 2023 Hamas attacks has evolved into a prolonged ground campaign, with significant humanitarian crisis in Gaza. The conflict has drawn in Hezbollah in Lebanon, Houthi forces in Yemen (attacking Red Sea shipping), and proxy groups across Syria and Iraq. Iran's direct missile strikes on Israel in April and October 2024 marked an unprecedented escalation in regional hostilities.</p>

      <div class="market-impact">
        <div class="market-impact-title">⚡ Market Impact — Israel-Gaza</div>
        <div class="impact-items">
          <div class="impact-item"><span class="impact-commodity">Crude Oil (Brent)</span><span class="impact-effect watch">+15-25% on escalation</span></div>
          <div class="impact-item"><span class="impact-commodity">Red Sea Shipping Costs</span><span class="impact-effect up">+200% rerouting premium</span></div>
          <div class="impact-item"><span class="impact-commodity">Israeli Shekel (ILS)</span><span class="impact-effect down">−12% vs USD since Oct '23</span></div>
          <div class="impact-item"><span class="impact-commodity">Israeli Tech Stocks (TA-125)</span><span class="impact-effect down">−18% from pre-war highs</span></div>
          <div class="impact-item"><span class="impact-commodity">Gold (safe haven)</span><span class="impact-effect up">+32% since Oct 2023</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
